---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects">
  <main>
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight mb-2">Projects</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle max-w-[38rem] mb-10">
      A selected set of things I have built across product engineering, internal tools, and personal experiments.
    </p>

    <div class="max-w-[38rem] space-y-10 text-[#2F2B26]">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-4">
          <img
            src="/projects/maia-dark.png"
            alt="Acme Analytics Platform"
            class="h-11 w-auto max-w-[240px] object-contain"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-[#2F2B26] prose-p:my-0 prose-p:mb-4 prose-p:text-[15px] prose-p:leading-7 prose-a:text-inherit prose-a:decoration-[var(--color-border)] prose-a:underline prose-a:underline-offset-4 hover:prose-a:text-[var(--color-brand)]">
          <p>
            A dashboard integrating with various data sources to visualize core startup metrics. It improved data transparency across non-technical teams and reduced ad-hoc data requests by 40%.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-[16px] leading-6 font-medium text-[#111111] mb-2">Personal Website</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-[#2F2B26] prose-p:my-0 prose-p:mb-4 prose-p:text-[15px] prose-p:leading-7 prose-a:text-inherit prose-a:decoration-[var(--color-border)] prose-a:underline prose-a:underline-offset-4 hover:prose-a:text-[var(--color-brand)]">
          <p>
            Built specifically to emphasize writing and reading over flashy UI cards. Heavy focus on performance and minimal visual noise. Source available on <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-[16px] leading-6 font-medium text-[#111111] mb-2">Markdown Notebook</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-[#2F2B26] prose-p:my-0 prose-p:mb-4 prose-p:text-[15px] prose-p:leading-7 prose-a:text-inherit prose-a:decoration-[var(--color-border)] prose-a:underline prose-a:underline-offset-4 hover:prose-a:text-[var(--color-brand)]">
          <p>
            Built to scratch my own itch for a note-taking application that doesn't rely on the cloud. It focuses heavily on keyboard navigation and sub-10ms response times for all rendering. The source is on <a href="https://github.com/example/md-notebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-0 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] opacity-90" />

      <section class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-[#2F2B26] prose-p:my-0 prose-p:mb-4 prose-p:text-[15px] prose-p:leading-7 prose-ul:my-0 prose-ul:pl-5 prose-li:my-0 prose-li:text-[15px] prose-li:leading-7 prose-a:text-inherit prose-a:decoration-[var(--color-border)] prose-a:underline prose-a:underline-offset-4 hover:prose-a:text-[var(--color-brand)]">
        <p>Fun projects with some original / innovative ideas:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ambient Reading Mode</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Notebook Search Lens</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Soft Focus Gallery</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Commit Review Playground</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Minimal Metrics Board</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-0 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] opacity-90" />

      <section class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-[#2F2B26] prose-p:my-0 prose-p:mb-4 prose-p:text-[15px] prose-p:leading-7 prose-ul:my-0 prose-ul:pl-5 prose-li:my-0 prose-li:text-[15px] prose-li:leading-7 prose-a:text-inherit prose-a:decoration-[var(--color-border)] prose-a:underline prose-a:underline-offset-4 hover:prose-a:text-[var(--color-brand)]">
        <p>My other mini projects (find all of them on <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>):</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Prompt Notebook</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Window Blur Study</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CLI Habit Tracker</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Diff Viewer</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tiny Markdown Renderer</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Queue App</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Annotation Tool</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
